//sign up component - used to sign up new user import { Component, OnInit } from '@angular/core'; import { NgForm } from '@angular/forms'; import { ActivatedRoute, Router } from '@angular/router'; import { AuthServiceService } from '../../auth-service.service'; @Component({ selector: 'app-signup', templateUrl: './signup.component.html', styleUrls: ['./signup.component.css'] }) export class SignupComponent implements OnInit{ //constructor constructor (public authservice: AuthServiceService, private router: Router) {} //initialization ngOnInit(): void {} //signup new user method onsignup(signupform: NgForm) { //input invalid if (signupform.invalid) { alert('Invalid') return } else { //sign up input valid this.authservice.signup( signupform.value.enteredUsername, signupform.value.enteredPassword, signupform.value.enteredFirstname, signupform.value.enteredLastname, signupform.value.enteredContact ) } } }

Sign Up

Username is required.
Username must start with an uppercase letter and can contain both letters and numbers. Length must be between 2 and 50.
Password is required.
Password must have a number, a lowercase letter, an uppercase letter, a special character and length must be between 3 and 50.
Firstname is required.
Firstname must start with an uppercase letter and can only contain letters. Length must be between 2 and 50.
Lastname is required.
Lastname must start with an uppercase letter and can only contain letters. Length must be between 2 and 50.
Contact is required.
Contact must be at least 1 character long.
